      <guid>http://localhost:1313/news/</guid>
      <description>&lt;section class=&#34;py-16 bg-gradient-to-b from-primary-50 to-white&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;container mx-auto px-4&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;max-w-6xl mx-auto text-center&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;h1 class=&#34;text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900&#34;&gt;News &amp; Events&lt;/h1&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;p class=&#34;text-xl text-neutral-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;            Stay updated with our latest research findings, upcoming conferences, and global initiatives in population health and social transformation&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/section&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;section class=&#34;py-12&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;container mx-auto px-4&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;max-w-6xl mx-auto&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;!-- Featured Research - Simplified --&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;div class=&#34;mb-16&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;            &lt;h2 class=&#34;text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-neutral-900&#34;&gt;Featured Research&lt;/h2&gt;&#xD;&#xA;            &#xD;&#xA;            &lt;div class=&#34;bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;                &lt;div class=&#34;bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-primary-700 p-6&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;                    &lt;div class=&#34;flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-3&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;                        &lt;span class=&#34;px-3 py-1 bg-white/20 text-white rounded-full text-sm font-medium&#34;&gt;NEW RESEARCH&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;                        &lt;span class=&#34;text-white/90 text-sm&#34;&gt;The British Journal of Sociology • 2025&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;                    &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;                    &lt;h3 class=&#34;text-2xl font-bold text-white&#34;&gt;Dependence and Precarity in the Gig Economy&lt;/h3&gt;&#xD;&#xA;                    &lt;p class=&#34;text-white/90 mt-2&#34;&gt;A Longitudinal Analysis of Platform Work and Mental Distress&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Policy Impact</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/policy/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/policy/</guid>
      <description>&lt;section class=&#34;py-16 bg-gradient-to-b from-primary-50 to-white&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;container mx-auto px-4&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;max-w-6xl mx-auto text-center&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;h1 class=&#34;text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-900&#34;&gt;Policy Impact&lt;/h1&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;p class=&#34;text-xl text-neutral-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;            Translating cutting-edge research into actionable policy recommendations for governments, organizations, and communities worldwide&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;/p&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/section&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;section class=&#34;py-12&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;container mx-auto px-4&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;max-w-6xl mx-auto&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;!-- Featured Story --&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;div class=&#34;mb-16&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;            &lt;div class=&#34;bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-primary-700 rounded-2xl p-1&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;                &lt;div class=&#34;bg-white rounded-2xl p-8&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;                    &lt;div class=&#34;flex items-center mb-4&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;                        &lt;span class=&#34;px-3 py-1 bg-danger-light text-danger-dark rounded-full text-sm font-medium&#34;&gt;FEATURED&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;                        &lt;span class=&#34;ml-3 text-neutral-500&#34;&gt;September 2025&lt;/span&gt;&#xD;&#xA;                    &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;                    &lt;h2 class=&#34;text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-neutral-900&#34;&gt;One Day of Work Per Week Sufficient for Mental Health Benefits&lt;/h2&gt;&#xD;&#xA;                    &#xD;&#xA;                    &lt;div class=&#34;grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;                        &lt;div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;                            &lt;p class=&#34;text-neutral-700 mb-4&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;                                Our groundbreaking research, conducted with the University of Cambridge, has redefined understanding of the relationship between work and wellbeing. The study of over 70,000 UK residents reveals that just 8 hours of work per week provides the full mental health benefits of employment.&#xD;&#xA;                            &lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Research</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/research/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/research/</guid>
      <description>&lt;section class=&#34;section&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;container&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;div class=&#34;text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;            &lt;h2 class=&#34;text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6&#34;&gt;Our Research Areas&lt;/h2&gt;&#xD;&#xA;            &lt;p class=&#34;text-xl text-gray-600&#34;&gt;We combine demographic science, computational methods, public health, and policy analysis to understand social change and design interventions that improve lives.&lt;/p&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;        &#xD;&#xA;        &lt;div class=&#34;space-y-32&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;            &#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center&#34; style=&#34;--badge-color: #ffffff&#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;    &#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;space-y-6 &#34;&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;style&gt;&#xD;&#xA;            .badge {&#xD;&#xA;                background-color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--badge-color) 10%, transparent);&#xD;&#xA;                color: var(--badge-color);&#xD;&#xA;            }&#xD;&#xA;            .badge-icon {&#xD;&#xA;                color: var(--badge-color);&#xD;&#xA;            }&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;/style&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;div class=&#34;badge inline-block px-4 py-2 rounded-full font-medium&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;h3 class=&#34;text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold&#34;&gt;Population Dynamics and Changes&lt;/h3&gt;&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;p class=&#34;text-lg text-gray-600&#34;&gt;We study fertility, mortality, aging, migration, and urbanization to understand how demographic shifts reshape societies, economies, and environments across regions.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
